      "id": "legend-content",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 915,
      "width": 919,
      "height": 59.99999999999999,
      "text": "🟢 Green = Channel Layer    🔵 Blue = Data/Container Layer    🟠 Orange = Queue/Scheduling    🔴 Red = Security (Credential Proxy)\n── Solid arrows = Data flow    ┄┄ Dashed arrows = Control flow / IPC",
